### **1. What is the total amount each customer spent at the restaurant?**
***sql syntax***
select 
  customer_id, 
  sum(price) as total_spending
from sales as s
join menu as m
on s.product_id = m.product_id
group by customer_id

***answear***
| customer_id | total_sales |
| ----------- | ----------- |
| A           | 76          |
| B           | 74          |
| C           | 36          |
